    I type here. Check out my <a href="http://tvtoday.20dots.com/" class="link-blue">latest app</a>. I'm a full stack <a href="http://rubyonrails.org/" class="link-blue">RoR</a> web developer with a bit of <a href="https://www.apple.com/swift/" class="link-blue">Swift</a> experience. Sometimes I <a href="https://soundcloud.com/arsvita" class="link-blue">make/mix music</a>.

  %ul.flex.flex-row.gap-x-6.md:flex-col.md:gap-y-8.md:pt-4
